Subject: FEATURE: add button to use speciesReference ids instead of stoichiometry
Date: Tue, 14 Sep 2010 10:37:09 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

When you press the "Use Mass Action" button, it uses the value of the  
stoiciometry in the kinetic law.  However, if the stoiciometry is  
changed by rules referencing the speciesReference id, then this is not  
correct.  Therefore, should add a button to use the speciesReference  
ids OR simply just use the speciesReference ids always.

